metadata.title: Ethereum Price Prediction After $3K Lost: What Happens to ETH DATs Now Paper Gains Are Gone?
metadata.description: The Ethereum price is down a further -9% in the past 24 hours, dropping to around $2,700, a level not seen since mid July, 2025, marking a four-month low for the second-largest digital asset by market cap. Technical indicators and institutional demand are leaning bearish, which could see ETH slip ...
